Name: Spencer Rd, Thornlie
Description: This intersection is notorious for vehicles running red lights.  They constantly fail to slow for the amber lights and the go through when the red is showing. The give way lanes often have vehicles fail to adhere to the give way sign.  They try to beat cars coming through the lights and vehicles behind other vehicles at the give way line fail to look in front of them before taking off and often hit hte car in the rear.
